&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Your future begins here! BGE, Inc&lt;strong&gt;.&lt;/strong&gt; is a nationwide civil engineering consulting firm offering diverse career opportunities in a wide range of disciplines for public and private infrastructure projects. Our employees enjoy a comprehensive benefits package that includes outstanding health care, generous 401(k) match, professional career resources, and highly competitive work-life balance programs, including personal-time allowances, dependent care, and flexible Fridays.&lt;/p&gt;
