&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a dedicated, detail-oriented CAD Designer to support civil site design projects for commercial, retail, and mixed-use developments. This role focuses on preparing accurate, code-compliant plans and construction documents using AutoCAD and Civil 3D, while collaborating closely with engineers and project managers to deliver high-quality site layouts, grading and drainage solutions, utility plans, and access improvements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
