&lt;li&gt;Cable schedules, tray, and conduit layouts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plot plans and electrical general arrangements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic 3D layouts and routing (cable tray, conduit, equipment)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
