&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with engineers and project managers to interpret design intent and translate engineering design into actionable deliverables.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in the development of electrical construction details and standard drawing libraries.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform drawing updates, redlines, as-builts, and document conversions as required for project delivery and digital engineering workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilize AutoCAD Electrical as the primary design tool; support additional platforms such as EPLAN, Bentley, and 3D modeling tools (e.g., CadWorx) as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with multidisciplinar

